General.Name: Sunland Group Ltd
General.Description: Sunland Group Limited develops and constructs residential properties in Australia. The company operates through two segments, Residential Housing and Urban Development, and Multi-Storey Development. The Residential Housing and Urban Development segment is involved in the land subdivision and medium density housing developments, as well as provides project services. The Multi-Storey segment develops and sells medium-rise projects between five and fifteen stories, and high-rise developments above fifteen stories. Sunland Group Limited was founded in 1983 and is based in Brisbane, Australia.
